公園でシャボン玉を追いかける子供たち。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kansas City" /><category term="Parks" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Kids chase bubbles in the park.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R07415.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2508_A7R07415.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shrine Morning・神社の朝</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250731/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shrine Morning・神社の朝" /><published>2025-07-31T00:00:00-07:00</published><updated>2025-07-31T00:00:00-07:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/anewday</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/250731/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
